{"tid":1733963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大學生會：校園有5百至6百人　六至七成是理大學生","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T08:36:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"059a61943bd5485ab9bef621ecc534327ace857a","tid":1733963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"理大學生會表示，現時校園已在危急關頭，呼籲全港市民協助理大師生，「救救理大、救救香港」。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會會長廖建鈞表示，現時仍有500至600人被困於校園內，相信有6至7成人士屬於理大學生。他說，由於兩小時前有示威者或學生再進入校園範圍，相信被困人數會有上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生校董李傲然說，警方在理工大學範圍施放多輪催淚彈，當中的有害物質水平未能預計，擔心事情持續發酵，理大校舍將不能繼續使用，造成不可逆轉傷害。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，據他所知，校長滕錦光除了清晨發放的錄像片段外，暫時未有任何表態，反映現時管理層對事件束手無策，對此感到極度失望。<br />\n<br />\n李傲然是區議會油尖旺大角咀北選區的候選人，同區另一候選人是民建聯劉柏祺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493001-20191118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493001-20191118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2eQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=a45a31d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493001-20191118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0d260dc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493001-20191118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c46beca3333721d93d0372ee6eb0900093ae1245","tid":1733963,"uid":338362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"221cf69a144557fb64294a97aa75cb814dea7530","tid":1733963,"uid":220766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"進入?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0b06c018c503405a63ea6e65b6aa796498f169","tid":1733963,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"愈多人形勢愈好 死守"},{"pid":"b6187789e066ec2f74cbc4442211853dc4ac4c99","tid":1733963,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95437b0f02430ef2c03de15db04f0aeb6d04592b","tid":1733963,"uid":55583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0b06c018c503405a63ea6e65b6aa796498f169","tid":1733963,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"愈多人形勢愈好 死守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"但愈多人就代表入面d資源消耗得愈快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae2dba90fc643a498f60a772b99d35109df8981","tid":1733963,"uid":314531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n全部人不論你是和理還是勇武 今晚終極對抗 如果你係為咗香港有民主！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"45e9cd230a93b84fb35da4fc12bf6085daa86ef2","tid":1733963,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"死守..."}]}